Package: epgwr
Type: Package
Title: Error Propagation in Geographically Weighted Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jaakko Madetoja
Maintainer: Jaakko Madetoja <jaakko.madetoja@aalto.fi>
Description: This package runs error propagation for a given Geographically Weighted Regression model using Monte Carlo simulation. The package also include functions for visualizing results with histograms and maps.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
